[Name] root-tail
[Summary] Allows printing of text directly to the X11 rootwindow
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] root-tail is a program that allows printing of text 
directly to the X11 root window wherever you 
choose, much like running rxvt with a pixmap 
background but without the hassle and with more 
features.
[Homepage] http://www.goof.com/pcg/marc/root-tail.html
